  Locus:
    Chapter: 6
    Paragraph: 73
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Great And Venerable Teacher
---
Confucius said, "If you're identical with it, you must have no more
likes! If you've been transformed, you must have no more constancy! So
you really are a worthy man after all!  With your permission, I'd
like to become your follower."
